text: Predeal () is a town in Brașov County, Romania. It is in the Prahova Valley. In 2021, 4,020 people lived there. Predeal is at an elevation of over . The town has three villages: Pârâul Rece, Timișu de Jos and Timișu de Sus. == References == == Other websites == * Category:Towns in Brașov County
